description: Operational metrics for Qlik Sense LAB

targets.query: SELECT count("message") AS "Errors" FROM "10d"."log_event" WHERE ("level" = 'WARN') AND (time > (now() - 1h)) GROUP BY time(1h)
SELECT count("message") AS "Errors" FROM "10d"."log_event" WHERE ("level" = 'WARN') AND (time > (now() - 1h)) GROUP BY time(1h)
SELECT count("message") AS "Errors" FROM "10d"."log_event" WHERE ("level" = 'ERROR') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(60m) ORDER BY time DESC

SELECT sum("total") 
FROM (
SELECT last("total") AS "total" FROM "session" WHERE ("qs_env"::tag = 'dev') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "server_description"::tag
)

SELECT sum("active") 
FROM (
SELECT last("active") AS "active" FROM "session" WHERE ("qs_env"::tag = 'dev') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "server_description"::tag
)
SELECT mean("session_count") FROM "user_session_summary" WHERE ("qs_env"::tag = 'prd') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "server_description" fill(none)

targets.query: SELECT sum("counter") FROM "event_count" WHERE ("qs_env"::tag = 'lab') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "source"::tag, "event_type"::tag, "subsystem"::tag, "host"::tag ORDER BY time DESC

panels.title: Received events

targets.query:
SELECT sum("EventCount") FROM (
  SELECT sum("counter") as "EventCount" FROM "event_count" WHERE  ("qs_env"::tag = 'lab') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "event_type"::tag, "event_name"::tag
) 
GROUP BY "event_name"

SELECT sum("EventCount") FROM (
  SELECT sum("counter") as "EventCount" FROM "event_count" WHERE  ("qs_env"::tag = 'dev') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "host"::tag, "event_name"::tag, "event_type"::tag, "subsystem"::tag
) 
GROUP BY "host"

SELECT sum("EventCount") FROM (
  SELECT sum("counter") as "EventCount" FROM "event_count" WHERE  ("qs_env"::tag = 'dev') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "host"::tag, "event_name"::tag, "event_type"::tag, "subsystem"::tag
) 
GROUP BY "event_type"

panels.title: Engine performance, end-user action: Monitored apps

targets.query:
SELECT count(distinct("app_id")) 
FROM (
SELECT count("counter") FROM "rejected_event_count" WHERE ("source"::tag = 'qseow-qix-perf' AND "app_name_set"::tag = 'true' AND "qs_env" = 'dev') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "app_name"::tag, "app_id"::tag
)

SELECT count("counter") FROM "rejected_event_count" WHERE ("source"::tag = 'qseow-qix-perf' AND "app_name_set"::tag = 'true' AND "qs_env" = 'dev') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval), "app_name"::tag, "app_id"::tag

panels.title: Unmonitored apps that have been accessed

targets.query: SELECT last("process_time") AS "Process time" FROM "rejected_event_count" WHERE ("source"::tag = 'qseow-qix-perf' AND "app_name_set"::tag = 'true' AND "app_name"::tag =~ /^$app_name_unmonitored$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "app_name"::tag, "method"::tag
